  <Strings>
    <Section>Story</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37208</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_002_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ヴァルハラか。なつかしいな〜</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Valhalla, huh? It brings back memories~</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <StructId>1</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>24</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37528</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_002_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>前来たのは……
仲間探してた時だったっけ…</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The last time we came here… was it when we were looking for our friends?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <StructId>2</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>24</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>37932</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_002_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……エトはまたいつか、
旅立っちゃうの……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Ethos, will you leave on another journey someday…?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <StructId>3</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>38772</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_002_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>仲間を探して？　うふふ、きみたちを
ほってどこかに行けるはずないでしょ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Looking for friends? Haha, there’s no way I’d leave you two behind and go somewhere else, right?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <StructId>4</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>24</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39668</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_002_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>本当に？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Really?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <StructId>5</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>39964</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_002_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ずっと一緒だよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We’ll always be together, okay?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <StructId>6</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>24</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>40264</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_002_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>マジで、&lt;MEL&gt;って
エトには甘えん坊だな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Seriously, &lt;MEL&gt;, you’re such a clingy kid when it comes to Ethos.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <StructId>7</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>12</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41288</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_002_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;DIO&gt;もでしょ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;DIO&gt;, you’re the same, aren’t you?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <StructId>8</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>13</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>41996</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;VCT_001_002_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……だってね……きみたちがいれば
他に仲間なんて必要ないかラ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Because, you know… as long as I have you two, I don’t need any other friends...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <StructId>9</StructId>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <UnknownPointer>24</UnknownPointer>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
